    About this hotel

    An 8-minute walk from Royal Country Club de Tanger, this upmarket hotel is 7 km from Plage Municipale (beach) and 12 km from Les Grottes d’Hercule (caves). …

    Featuring free Wi-Fi and balconies, the stylish rooms come with flat-screen TVs, minibars and in-room safes. Room service is available 24/7.

    Free breakfast is served in an airy restaurant, and parking is available at no charge. There’s also a hip piano bar. Amenities include an outdoor pool and a fitness room, as well as a spa area with a sauna and hammam. Massage treatments and an airport shuttle are offered, both for a fee.
